To compile: run ./build or use go-gb.
To run: execute ./_bin/main inside the examples folder.

settings.json can be changed to change the resolution and the save directory.

Flags: run "./_bin/main -help" for more information.

Controls:
     'P': pause/resume
     'S': advance by a single frame when paused
    'F5': save to ./saves/quicksave.json
    'F9': load from ./saves/quicksave.json
'Escape': close the application

Console commands:
"save <file>" saves the scene to "./saves/<file>"
"load <file>" loads from "./saves/<file>"
"help" lists all available commands
